{"tid":1431913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，我哋未來見","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:58:32.000Z","uid":228945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc3c3505aeef3f9fcb11e48c114d6c207ae069e","tid":1431913,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:58:32.000Z","msg":"雖然琴晚喺尖沙咀好開心，<br />\n我自己睇live都feel到個氣氛好正，<br />\n或者呢個moment只係一個喘息，<br />\n但我相信，<br />\n終有一日，<br />\n我哋各位會除低口罩，<br />\n喺煲底、尖沙咀，<br />\n一齊玩laser，<br />\n一齊唱歌、跳舞。<br />\n<br />\n高峰的風景多美好<br />\n也共遍 踏塵跟土<br />\n在這秒鐘 仍一起看夕陽<br />\n約定 未知那遠路裡<br />\n同看著時代飛舞<br />\n<br />\n香港人，我哋未來見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Hroq64h65Os\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHroq64h65Os&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=244c76d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Hroq64h65Os</a>"}]}